    "The LSTM model easily handles the longer-range dependencies, and they do not easily fall into the gradient vanishing issues.",
    "They also resolve complicated sequential information.",
    "Moreover, the developed AH-CNN-LSTM techniques tackled several limitations attained in the training procedures and also eased the motion intention prediction process.",
    "The efficiency of the motion intention prediction is improved by optimizing several parameters in the developed AH-CNN-LSTM model by IYSGA.",
    "In this implemented AH-CNN-LSTM model, the hidden neuron counts in CNN and LSTM techniques and also the epoch counts in CNN and LSTM models are optimized using IYSGA."
